《'''夹边沟'''》是中国大陆导演[[王兵_(导演)|王兵]]的第一部故事片，于2010年9月6日在威尼斯电影节首映。<ref>{{Cite news|title=《告别夹边沟》威尼斯获好评 将角逐金狮奖|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/idCNCHINA-2961920100907|newspaper=Reuters|date=2010-09-07|accessdate=2021-09-29|language=en|archive-date=2021-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210929071337/https://www.reuters.com/article/idCNCHINA-2961920100907|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=王兵新作《夹边沟》威尼斯最“惊喜”(组图)-搜狐娱乐|url=https://yule.sohu.com/20100908/n274781319.shtml|access-date=2021-09-29|date=2010-09-08|work=搜狐|publisher=[[东方早报|东方早报]]|language=zh|archive-date=2021-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210929071141/https://yule.sohu.com/20100908/n274781319.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=《夹边沟》亮相逐金狮 华语影人成威尼斯主角|url=https://xian.qq.com/a/20100907/000333.htm|access-date=2021-09-29|date=2010-09-07|work=|publisher=腾讯大秦网|language=zh|archive-date=2021-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210929072443/https://xian.qq.com/a/20100907/000333.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=电影《夹边沟》亮相水城 入围威尼斯电影节主竞赛单元_娱乐频道_凤凰网|url=https://ent.ifeng.com/movie/news/occident/detail_2010_09/09/2469679_0.shtml|access-date=2021-09-29|date=2010-09-09|work=凤凰网|publisher=兰州晚报|language=zh|archive-date=2021-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210929071151/https://ent.ifeng.com/movie/news/occident/detail_2010_09/09/2469679_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>影片根据[[楊顯惠|楊顯惠]]的小说《[[告别夹边沟|告别夹边沟]]》中的片段改编，以中国甘肃右派劳改农场为背景，描绘了右派分子被强制劳动改造、饥饿而死的悲惨景象。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://biweekly.hrichina.org/article/787 |publisher= |title=历史没有音乐——关于电影《夹边沟》 |journal= |author=[[余世存|余世存]]|access-date=2014-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108174228/http://biweekly.hrichina.org/article/787 |archive-date=2014-01-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>该片曾在法国[[德法公共电视台|Arte台]]播放<ref>{{cite web |url = http://videos.arte.tv/fr/videos/_le_fosse_de_wang_bing-3412586.html |title = "Le fossé" de Wang Bing - videos.arte.tv |date = 2010-09-07 |